				<p>Also [this](http://web.eecs.utk.edu/~leparker/Courses/CS594-fall08/Lectures/Nov-13-Localization-Mapping-I.pdf) could be helpful... or just start with [this](https://www.google.ca/search?q=what+is+the+problem+with+dead+reckoning&ie=utf-8&oe=utf-8&gws_rd=cr&ei=-HleVrXqHMS6ebPDiMgO#safe=off&q=robot+dead+reckoning+localization+error+why).</p>
