				<p>Yes, therefore we need an external setup to do this. That is actually the purpose of my question. What kind of external setup that will allow me to measure the actual speed reliably without the use of expensive equipments? Like I said, I can think of using an ultrasonic sensor to do this. Are there other better ways to do it?</p>
			</div>
